description: Midway Holding AB engages in the acquisition and investment of small and medium enterprises. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane and currently employs 1,025 full-time employees.  The firm reports two divisions, namely Technology and Trade. The Technology division groups the Company’s subsidiaries active within the construction supplies and industrial electronics sectors, such as Landqvist Mekaniska AB, Fas Converting Machinery AB, Haki AB and MidTrailer AB. The Trade division groups the Company’s subsidiaries active within the automotive, construction machinery, business solutions and communications equipment sectors, such as Gustaf E Bil AB and NOM Holding AS. The firm operates primarily in Sweden and other Scandinavian countries.
name: Midway Holding AB
